{
  "stem": "5810.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It's-- it's a design; looks like a flower.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And every time I woke up screaming, my wife tells me, it was always with that image in mind.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I was always wondering what it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And now, I came to find out, because I did visit the Barniche after the war-- many years after the war--I think about 30 years after the war; it took me that long to have the guts to do that-- was that the little horse-drawn carriage that I always wanted that he had given to his son [? who has ?] denied me.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And that some reason it made such an impression on me that it continued right onto my adulthood and after the war as being one of the images that was very, very strong, and woke up in-- in cold sweat and screams.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But our lives there, all I can remember is that this is, in my young years, this is the first time I wished for being taken or dying, and no longer having this nightmare.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And seeing my mother that way, it was just the most awful thing there was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But there was so many things in between that that happened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[SIGHS] As I said, the monies that were either paid by the underground wasn't enough.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we were paying them monthly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And that was dwindling.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a gold coin, I remember, on a monthly basis.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's the one thing I couldn't even begin to tell you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't even know what the gold coins, from what country they were.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just remembered these gold coins.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Which, to go back somewhat-- some-- I buried in the garden of the house-- we-- the house that was denied back to us by those gentiles.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
